    {
      "id": "80",
      "name": "Properties",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Relationships",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4897,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/08/237301566/513d51e0ebfd54f5da34a9f85dfaf61f_4818954959690057221.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Изначальный",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Heavenly Principles invaded Teyvat and declared war on the ancient elemental dragons. Forty years later, the seven Dragon Sovereigns were defeated and the seven nations submitted to the Primordial One. The First Throne stole the authority of the elemental dragons to create the divine thrones.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7083,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Ангелы",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7082,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Феи",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Some angels and Seelie resisted the dragons. In Natlan, almost all angels and Seelie were destroyed.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Archons",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Dragons consider the Archons as usurpers.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4780,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2023/12/20/a5b8d23dd3fbe0969cc3ebce78f9c29f_8021351765588020911.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Эгерия",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When the first Hydro Dragon was killed, Celestia created Egeria to be the heart of the Primordial Sea. When Egeria was in the Primordial Sea, a new Hydro Dragon couldn't be reborn.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4781,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2023/12/20/0c738427840832159123453a49753e8f_3478299024622747823.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Фокалорс",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The last Hydro Archon destroyed the divine throne and returned the dragon's authority to the Hydro Dragon.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4903,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/20/237301566/206a8a0bc1698ae7019f093470f9e845_1446865023244996257.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Дурин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Shadow dragon from the Abyss, created by",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 6368,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/28/237301566/b12de89916409eae3b0325ed5432efc4_7390281426362006143.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Рэйндоттир",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Although he is called a dragon, he belongs to the Void Realm and is not from a dragon race.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4914,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/02/237301566/fa4c986eefe97522566b35be6e29e7a0_471244222089785302.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Элинас",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Dragonlike creature, brother of Durin and son of Rhinedottir. He belongs to the Void Realm and is not from a dragon race.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Seven Dragon Sovereigns",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7489,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/03/237301566/596896f7ea3d51d7b1f6e504094f9d97_4010709984094972573.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Nibelung",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Dragon King, leader of the elemental dragons. When the Primordial One won the war, Nibelung acquired the power of darkness from outside of this world and led the dragons in a fight against the order established by the outsiders.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4913,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/01/03/9750d15029b9018793ef9d9f0bfec6de_743071265959457769.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Апеп",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Dendro Sovereign who ruled Sumeru. She stayed loyal to Nibelung and attempted to collect more forbidden knowledge from the corners of the world but was stopped by the giant spike that fell from the sky. Apep made a deal with",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 4911,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/18/237301566/513d51e0ebfd54f5da34a9f85dfaf61f_8921855237440624526.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Al-Ahmar",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "that after his death, all the knowledge he came to accumulate would belong to her. As Al-Ahmar was corrupted with the forbidden knowledge, Apep also got corrupted. Thousands of years later, she was healed by the Dendro Archon.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "First Hydro Dragon",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A heart of the Primordial Sea, that was destroyed by the first throne.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4023,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/24/70239714/0513aa7f482dbb4778545d02f94956fe_5004007435087179259.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Нёвиллет",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The reborn Hydro Dragon, who gained his full authority after the Hydro divine throne was destroyed.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7298,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/12/02/237301566/36590cd4be92a9d70abed92915537d5e_3879864065456128285.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Xiuhcoatl",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Flamelord, who was defeated by the first Pyro Archon,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7074,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/08/237301566/e7f7eee058f60fc225b1f5bc654a08e0_7006634286090563879.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Шбаланке",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Notable Dragons",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4784,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2023/12/20/472a219c5d998c371672b670a0829f16_7380212387492663867.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Аждаха",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Geo Dragon Lord, whom the Geo Archon, Morax, gave the eyes. Azhdaha helped the people of Liyue for many years until his consciousness was damaged by erosion.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "It is unknown if Azhdaha is a Geo Sovereign.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4902,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/20/237301566/b6e31b3c3cb069320d40e3b7b7d06b2f_2627257747151251085.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Двалин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "An elemental dragon of the wind, a friend of the Anemo Archon, Barbatos. He is one of the Four Winds and the protector of Mondstadt.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "It is unknown if Dvalin is an Anemo Sovereign.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5619,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/01/237301566/b2d6cefc957361355bd202af3efcb21d_4484292652819500070.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Сцилла",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The dragon prince who led the army of the Fontemer's Vishaps until the Hydro Dragon could be reborn.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "K'uhul Ajaw",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A self-proclaimed \"Divine Lord,\" a bona fide relic from the era of dragons, dating back several millennia. His true form has been sealed within an enigmatic engraved wristband, his current one being a mere projection via phlogiston. K'uhul Ajaw signed an unbreakable pact with",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 6317,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/15/70239714/9b80ee75a81f8c4c9148a8fea589ccbc_5880057952609706718.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Кинич",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "that the dragon would lend his power to Kinich. In exchange, Kinich would take Ajaw out to see the outside world, and upon his passing, his body would be Ajaw's to take for his own use.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7297,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/04/03/237301566/b9c40708c129547b244f252d9b749a86_6061004772219375990.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Waxaklahun Ubah Kan",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A dragon who stole the phlogiston from his kind and taught humans how to use it. He tried to create a ruler who would be stronger than the Heavenly Principles and the dragons.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ix Uxul Tz'ib Bolon Ch'ule-L",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Type-L Self-Regulating Overseer Array Integrated Processing Unit, the Dragonlord of Chichen Uctokah.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ursa the Drake",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A dragon that terrorized Mondstadt for over a thousand years. It was defeated by the Fatui Harbinger, Dottore.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
